# Object Property: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> "Example:
Aggregate of Rock Bodies bounds a Trap"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> "Exemplo:
Agregado de Corpos de Rocha delimitando uma Armadilha."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> "bounds"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> "delimita"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> "Indica que uma entidade delimita outra entidade."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> "Indicates that one entity delimits another entity."@en)
ObjectPropertyDomain(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies>)
ObjectPropertyRange(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap>)

# Object Property: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> "Example:
Oil and Natural Gas are contained within a rock layer."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> "Exemplo:
Oleo e Gás Natural estão contidos em uma camamada de rocha."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> "contained in"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> "contido en"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> "Indica que uma entidade está contida em outra entidade."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> "Indicates that one entity is contained within another entity."@en)
ObjectPropertyDomain(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> <https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000006>)
ObjectPropertyRange(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> <https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000001>)

# Object Property: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> "Exemplo:
Folhelho tem alta concentração de matéria orgânica."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> "alta concentração de"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> "hight concentration of"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> "Example:
Shale has a high concentration of organic matter."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> "Indica que um material terrestre possui alta concentração de outro material."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> "Indicates that an Earth material contains a high concentration of another material."@en)
SubObjectPropertyOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> owl:topObjectProperty)
ObjectPropertyDomain(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter>)
ObjectPropertyRange(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter>)



############################
#   Classes
############################

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> (natural gas)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> "Example: Natural gas is generated from organic matter."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> "Exemplo: 
O gás natural que é gerado a partir da matéria orgânica."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> "gás natural"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> "natural gas"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> "Gás Natural é uma especialização de petróleo cuja matéria se apresenta no estado gasoso em condições de superfície, podendo ser de origem termogênica ou biogênica."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> "Natural Gas is a specialization of petroleum whose material is present in a gaseous state under surface conditions and may originate from thermogenic or biogenic processes."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Natural_Gas> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> (óleo)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> "Example: 
Oil migrates upward through permeable layers."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> "Exemplo: 
O óleo que migra para cima através de camadas permeável."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> "oil"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> "óleo"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> "Oil is a hydrocarbon whose matter is in a liquid state at surface conditions, being a thermally generated hydrocarbon from organic matter within a specific thermal window."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> "Óleo é um hidrocarboneto cuja matéria se apresenta no estado líquido em condições de superfície, sendo um hidrocarboneto gerado termicamente a partir da matéria orgânica em uma janela térmica específica."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Oil> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#contained_in> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> (seal)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> "Example:
Sealing capacity is a disposition related to geological objects such as evaporite layers and compact shales."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> "seal"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> "selo"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> "Seal is a disposition inhering in a rock layer that confers the capacity to prevent or significantly restrict the migration of hydrocarbons owing to its low permeability and high capillary entry pressure."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> "Selo é uma disposição de uma camada de rocha  que confere a capacidade de impedir ou restringir o fluxo vertical de hidrocarbonetos devido à sua permeabilidade  baixa  e alta pressão de entrada."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000016>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> "Example: 
Accumulation is a Geological Process such as stratigraphic accumulation and structural accumulation."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> "Exemplo:
Acumulação é um Processo Geológico como acumulação estratigráfica e acumulação estrutural."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> "accumulation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> "acumulação"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> "Accumulation is the final event in which migrated hydrocarbons become concentrated within a geological trap, overlain by a rock layer bearing a seal disposition, thereby forming a hydrocarbon accumulation or field."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> "Acumulação é um evento final no qual os hidrocarbonetos migrados são concentrados em uma armadilha geológica, sobrepostos por uma rocha com disposição selo, formando um campo ou acumulação."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Process>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> "Aggregate of Rock Bodies"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> "agregado de rochas"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> "Agregado de Corpos de Rocha é um Object Aggregate  que reúne múltiplos corpos de rocha com limites definidos, como uma unidade litoestratigráfica composta ou um conjunto de camadas em uma bacia."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> "An Aggregate of Rocks Bodies is an Object Aggregate that comprises multiple rock bodies with defined boundaries, such as a composite lithostratigraphic unit or a set of layers within a basin."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000027>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#hasPart> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#aggregate_of_rock_bodies> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#bounds> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> (basalt)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> "Example: 
Basalt is an Earth Material such as vesicular basalt and massive basalt."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> "Exemplo: 
Basalto é um Material Terrestre como basalto vesicular e basalto maciço."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> "basalt"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> "basalto"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> "Basalt is an igneous rock formed by the rapid cooling of lava at the Earth's surface or on the ocean floor."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> "Basalto é uma rocha ígnea, resultante do resfriamento rápido de lava na superfície terrestre ou no assoalho oceânico."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> "Example: 
Basin is a Geological Object such as intracratonic basins and rift basins."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> "Exemplo:
Bacia é um Objeto Geológico como bacias intracratônicas e bacias rifte."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> "bacia"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> "basin"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> "A Basin is a rock body corresponding to a long-lived topographic depression filled with sedimentary rocks and formed by tectonic processes."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> "Bacia é um corpo de rocha que corresponde a uma depressão topográfica de longa duração preenchida por rochas sedimentares, formada por processos tectônicos."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basin> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> "Example:
A rock body such as layers and dikes."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> "Exemplo: 
Um corpo de rocha como camadas e diques."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> "body of rock"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> "corpo de rocha"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> "Body of Rock is a geological object consisting of a continuous and spatially bounded volume of rock, generated by one or more geological processes and capable of being mapped as a lithostratigraphic or tectonic unit."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> "Corpo de Rocha é um objeto geológico que consiste em um volume contínuo e espacialmente delimitado de rocha, gerado por um ou mais processos geológicos, podendo ser mapeado como uma unidade litoestratigráfica ou tectônica."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock> <https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000001>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> "Example:
Dikes are geological objects, such as basaltic dikes."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> "Exemplo:
Diques são Objetos Geológicos como diques basálticos."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> "dikes"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> "diques"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> "Dikes are tabular, discordant rock bodies formed by the intrusion of igneous rock."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> "Diques são corpos de rocha tabulares, discordantes, resultantes da intrusão de rocha ígnea."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000017> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#basalto>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> "generation"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> "geração"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> "Generation is an event in which the organic matter contained within a rock layer bearing a source disposition is thermally or biologically transformed into hydrocarbons under specific pressure and temperature conditions."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> "Geração é um evento no qual a matéria orgânica contida em uma rocha com disposição de geradora é termicamente ou biologicamente convertida em hidrocarbonetos, sob condições específicas de pressão e temperatura."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Process>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000063> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> "Example: 
Igneous Rock is an Earth Material such as basalt."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> "Exemplo: 
Rocha Ígnea é um Material Terrestre como basalto."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> "igneas rock"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> "rocha ígnea"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> "Igneous rock is a rock formed by the cooling and solidification of magma or lava, whose texture and mineral composition reflect the thermal history of its crystallization."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> "Rocha Ígnea é uma rocha formada pelo resfriamento e solidificação do magma ou lava, cuja textura e composição mineral refletem a história térmica de sua cristalização."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#igneas_rock> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> "Example:
A layer is a rock body, such as shale layers and sandstone layers."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> "Exemplo: 
Camada é um Corpo de Rocha como camadas de folhelho e camadas de arenito."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> "camada"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> "layer"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> "A Layer is a rock body characterized by a tabular or lens-shaped geometry, distinguished by physical discontinuities that define its upper and lower boundaries. It represents the basic unit of stratigraphic sequences and may be composed of different rock types."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> "Camada é um corpo de rocha que possui formato de camada ou de lente, sendo individualizado por descontinuidades físicas que constituem seus limites superior e inferior. Ele representa a unidade básica das sequências estratigráficas e pode ser composto por diferentes tipos de rocha."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#body_of_rock>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> "Example: Limestone is an Earth Material such as fossiliferous limestone and micritic limestone."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> "Exemplo: 
Calcário é um Material Terrestre como calcário fossilífero e calcário micrítico."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> "calcário"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> "limestone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> "Calcário é uma rocha sedimentar constituída predominantemente por carbonato de cálcio, geralmente de origem biogênica ou química, podendo atuar como reservatório ou rocha selante."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> "Limestone is a sedimentary rock composed predominantly of calcium carbonate, typically of biogenic or chemical origin."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> "camada de calcário"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> "limestone layer"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> "A Limestone Layer is a layer constituted by limestone."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> "Camada de Calcário é uma camada constituída por calcário."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000017> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> "Example: 
Migration is a Geological Process such as primary migration and secondary migration."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> "Exemplo:
 Migração é um Processo Geológico como migração primária e migração secundária."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> "migration"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> "migração"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> "Migration is an event in which generated hydrocarbons are naturally transported from a rock layer bearing a source disposition through a reservoir rock or fracture system toward a trap."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> "Migração é um evento no qual os hidrocarbonetos gerados são transportados naturalmente desde a rocha com disposição geradora através de uma rocha reservatório ou sistema de fraturas  até uma armadilha."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Process>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#migration> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000063> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#accumulation>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> (organic matter)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> "Example:
Organic matter contained in shale layers."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> "Exemplo: 
A matéria orgânica contida em camadas de folhelhos."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> "Matéria Orgânica"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> "organic matter"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> "Matéria Orgânica é um material da terra constituído por compostos derivados de organismos vivos, depositado em ambientes sedimentares, que sob condições adequadas de pressão e temperatura transforma-se em hidrocarbonetos."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> "Organic Matter is an Earth Material composed of compounds derived from living organisms, deposited in sedimentary environments, which under suitable pressure and temperature conditions transforms into hydrocarbons."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> <https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000006>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> "permeabilidade"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> "permeability"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> "Permeabilidade é uma qualidade que representa a capacidade do material rochoso de transmitir fluidos através de sua rede de poros interconectados."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> "Permeability is a quality that represents the ability of a rock material to transmit fluids through its network of interconnected pore spaces."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> (petroleum)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> "Example: 
Petroleum accumulates in the pores of a reservoir rock."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> "Exemplo: 
O petróleo acumulado nos poros de uma rocha reservatório."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> "petroleum"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> "petróleo"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> "Petroleum is an Earth Fluid that constitutes a natural mixture of hydrocarbon compounds, occurring in gaseous, liquid, or solid states, genetically related to an active source rock."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> "Petróleo é um tipo de  fluido da terra, que constitui uma mistura natural de compostos de hidrocarbonetos, de ocorrência gasosa, líquida ou sólida, geneticamente relacionada a uma rocha geradora ativa."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> <https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000009>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#petroleum> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000013> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#generation>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> "Example:
Porosity is a quality of Earth materials, such as intergranular porosity."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> "Exemplo: 
Porosidade é uma Qualidade de Materiais Terrestres como porosidade intergranular."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> "porosidade"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> "porosity"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> "Porosity is a quality inhering in a rock body that is defined as the fraction of its total volume occupied by void spaces."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> "Porosity é uma qulalidade, definida como a fração do volume total da rocha ocupada por espaços vazios ."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> "pressure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> "pressão"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> "Pressure is a quality inhering in a rock body or fluid that quantifies the force exerted per unit area and plays an essential role in the generation, migration, and retention of hydrocarbons."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> "Pressão é uma qualidade que quantifica a força aplicada por unidade de área sobre um corpo de rocha ou fluido, sendo um fator essencial para os processos de geração, migração e retenção de hidrocarbonetos."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> "reservatório"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> "reservoir"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> "Reservatório é uma disposição de uma camada de rocha que confere a capacidade de armazenar e transmitir fluidos por meio de sua porosidade e permeabilidade efetivas."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> "Reservoir is a disposition inhering in a rock layer that confers the capacity to store and transmit fluids through its effective porosity and permeability."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000016>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> "Example:
A quantity of rock present in a sedimentary basin."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> "Exemplo:
 Uma quantidade de rocha presente em um  bacia sedimentar."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> "rocha"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> "rock"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> "Rocha é um material da terra, que não possui critério de unidade próprio, sendo sua identidade definida por composição e origem."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> "Rock is an Earth material that lacks its own unity criterion, with its identity being determined by its composition and origin."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock> <https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000006>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> "Example: 
Sandstone is an Earth Material such as quartzose sandstone and feldspathic sandstone."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> "Exemplo:
 Arenito é um Material Terrestre como arenito quartzoso e arenito feldspático."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> "arenito"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> "sandstone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> "Arenito é uma rocha sedimentar composta por grãos de areia cimentados, caracterizada por porosidade e permeabilidade intergranulares."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> "Sandstone is a sedimentary rock composed of cemented sand-sized grains, characterized by intergranular porosity and permeability."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> "camada de arenito"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> "sandstone layer"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> "A Sandstone Layer is a layer constituted by sandstone."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> "Camada de Arenito é uma camada constituída por arenito."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000017> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sandstone_layer> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#limestone_layer> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> "Example:
The amount of sedimentary rock in depositional environments."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> "Exemplo: 
Quantidade de rocha sedimentar em ambientes deposicionais."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24.

Abel, M., Perrin, M., & Carbonera, J. L. (2015). Ontological analysis for information integration in geomodeling. Earth Science Informatics, 8(1), 21-36."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> "rocha sedimentar"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> "sedimentary rock"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> "Rocha que é gerada por um Processo Geológico de sedimentação, envolvendo a deposição e a cimentação de partículas minerais ou orgânicas na superfície ou próximo à superfície da Terra."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> "Rock that is generated by a Geological Process of sedimentation, involving the deposition and cementation of mineral or organic particles on or near the Earth's surface."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#rock>)

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> "Example:
Shale is an Earth Material such as black shale and siliceous shale."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> "Exemplo: 
Folhelho é um Material Terrestre como folhelho negro e folhelho silicoso"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> "folhelho"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> "shalee"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> "Folhelho é uma rocha sedimentar fina, laminada, composta por partículas de tamanho argila e silte, rica em matéria orgânica."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> "Shale is a fine-grained, laminated sedimentary rock composed of clay- and silt-sized particles and enriched in organic matter."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#sedimentary_rock>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#high_concetration_of> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#organic_matter>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> "camada de folhelho"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> "shale layer"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> "A Shale Layer is a layer constituted by shale."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> "Camada de Folhelho  é uma camada constituída por folhelho."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000196> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale_layer> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000017> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#shale>))
