# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> "Example:
Source potential is a disposition related to organic matter-rich shales and mudstones."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> "Exemplo
Geradora é uma disposiçãol relacionada a como folhelhos e lamitos ricos em matéria orgânica."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> "geradoura"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> "source"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> "Geradora é uma disposição de uma camada de rocha que, sob condições específicas de pressão e temperatura, confere a capacidade de gerar e expelir hidrocarbonetos a partir da matéria orgânica nela contida."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> "Source is a disposition inhering in a rock layer that, under specific pressure and temperature conditions, confers the capacity to generate and expel hydrocarbons from the organic matter contained within it."@en)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000016>)
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#source> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#Seal> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#reservoir>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> "Example: 
Temperature is a quality inherent in geological objects, such as geothermal temperature."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> "Exemplo:
Temperatura é uma Qualidade que inere em Objetos Geológicos como temperatura geotérmica ."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> "temperatura"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> "temperature"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> "Temperature is a quality inhering in a material entity that represents the measure of the average kinetic energy of its constituent particles."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> "Temperature é uma qualidade, representando a medida da energia cinética média das partículas constituintes."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000197> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>))
DisjointClasses(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#temperature> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#permeability> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#porosity> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#pressure>))

# Class: <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> (<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap>)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> "Example:
Trap is a Geological Structure such as anticlinal traps and fault traps."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> "Exemplo: 
Armadilha é uma Estrutura Geológica como armadilhas anticlinais e armadilhas de falha."@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> "Reference:
L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow, The petroleum system, in: L. B. Magoon, W. G. Dow (Eds.), The Petroleum System: From Source to Trap, volume 60 of AAPG Memoir, American Association of Petroleum Geologists, Tulsa, Oklahoma, 1994, pp. 3–24."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> "armadilha"@pt-br)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> "trap"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> "A Trap is a geological structure that defines a tectonic or stratigraphic geometry and is materialized in one or more rock bodies."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> "Armadilha é uma estrutura geológica  que configura uma geometria tectônica ou estratigráfica, materializada em um ou mais corpos rochosos."@pt-br)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> <https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/bdi/ontologies/GEOCORE_0000004>)
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#hasPart> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#dikes>))
SubClassOf(<http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#trap> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#hasPart> <http://www.semanticweb.org/gustavo/ontologies/2026/5/untitled-ontology-3#layer>))


